var richText1 = /* @__PURE__ */ e(t.Fragment, { children: /* @__PURE__ */ e("p", { children: "With product photography, clarity is key. This shoot was designed for a brand launch, so every image needed to be consistent, high-resolution, and visually striking. I chose a neutral palette and simple backgrounds to let the product shine. Every angle was carefully considered to highlight texture, function, and form. Lighting was diffused to avoid harsh reflections while maintaining crisp detail. Whether used for a website, social media, or print, these visuals are built to convert \u2014 clean, professional, and on-brand. The goal was not just to photograph a product, but to communicate its value in a glance." }) });
var richText2 = /* @__PURE__ */ e(t.Fragment, { children: /* @__PURE__ */ e("p", { children: "Urban architecture often gets overlooked in day-to-day life, but through the lens, it becomes art. This series explores geometric forms, lines, and shadow play found in modern cityscapes. I aimed to strip away distractions and highlight the beauty of structure \u2014 glass facades, sharp corners, and bold concrete walls. Most photos were taken during early morning or late afternoon, when directional light added depth and drama to each frame. The final collection speaks to a minimalist aesthetic \u2014 clean, crisp, and perfectly aligned. Ideal for design lovers or brands that celebrate structure and modernism." }) });
var richText3 = /* @__PURE__ */ e(t.Fragment, { children: /* @__PURE__ */ e("p", { children: "Portrait photography is all about connection \u2014 between subject, space, and light. In this shoot, I embraced the golden hour glow to capture honest, emotive portraits that feel intimate yet editorial. I worked with natural light only, letting the warm tones wrap gently around the subject\u2019s face, enhancing their features without the need for heavy post-processing. By keeping the background clean and the posing minimal, each image draws focus to subtle expressions and mood. The result is a timeless set that balances softness and strength \u2014 perfect for personal branding or lifestyle features." }) });
